itle=Weekly Top 30 Programmes: Week Ending 24 Oct 2010\u201317 Apr 2011|accessdate=26 April 2011|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5wSLX6Azh?url=http://www.barb.co.uk/report/weeklyTopProgrammesOverview|archivedate=13 February 2011|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 14)|14]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|2011|10|18|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2012|10|9|df=y}}\n! 4.92<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.barb.co.uk/whats-new/weekly-top-30?|publisher=[[Broadcasters' Audience Research Board]]|title=Weekly Top 30 Programmes: Week Ending 23 Oct 2011\u201314 Oct 2012|accessdate=22 February 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5wSLX6Azh?url=http://www.barb.co.uk/report/weeklyTopProgrammesOverview|archivedate=13 February 2011|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 15)|15]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|2012|10|16|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2013|10|8|df=y}}\n! 4.61<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.barb.co.uk/whats-new/weekly-top-30?|publisher=[[Broadcasters' Audience Research Board]]|title=Weekly Top 30 Programmes: Week Ending 21 Oct 2012\u201313 Oct 2013|accessdate=22 February 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5wSLX6Azh?url=http://www.barb.co.uk/report/weeklyTopProgrammesOverview|archivedate=13 February 2011|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 16)|16]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|2013|10|15|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2014|10|7|df=y}}\n! 4.38<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.barb.co.uk/whats-new/weekly-top-30?|publisher=[[Broadcasters' Audience Research Board]]|title=Weekly Top 30 Programmes: Week Ending 20 Oct 2013\u201312 Oct 2014|accessdate=22 February 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5wSLX6Azh?url=http://www.barb.co.uk/report/weeklyTopProgrammesOverview|archivedate=13 February 2011|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 17)|17]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|2014|10|14|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2015|10|6|df=y}}\n! 4.64<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.barb.co.uk/whats-new/weekly-top-30?|publisher=[[Broadcasters' Audience Research Board]]|title=Weekly Top 30 Programmes: Week Ending 19 Oct 2014\u201311 Oct 2015|accessdate=22 February 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5wSLX6Azh?url=http://www.barb.co.uk/report/weeklyTopProgrammesOverview|archivedate=13 February 2011|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 18)|18]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|2015|10|13|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2016|10|4|df=y}}\n! 4.53<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.barb.co.uk/whats-new/weekly-top-30?|publisher=[[Broadcasters' Audience Research Board]]|title=Weekly Top 30 Programmes: Week Ending 18 Oct 2015\u201309 Oct 2016|accessdate=9 November 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5wSLX6Azh?url=http://www.barb.co.uk/report/weeklyTopProgrammesOverview|archivedate=13 February 2011|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|{{Refn|name=Eight|Based on twenty-eight-day data.|group=nb}}\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 19)|19]]\n| 64\n| {{Start date|2016|10|11|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2017|12|19|df=y}}\n! 4.54<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web |url=http://www.barb.co.uk/whats-new/weekly-top-30?|publisher=[[Broadcasters' Audience Research Board]]|title=Weekly Top 30 Programmes: Week Ending 18 Oct 2015\u201309 Oct 2016|accessdate=24 January 2018}}</ref>\n|{{Refn|name=Eight|Based on twenty-eight-day data.|group=nb}}\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 20)|20]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|2018|01|02|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2018|12|27|df=y}}\n| <!--<ref name=\"auto\"/>-->\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 21)|21]]\n| 53\n| {{Start date|2019|01|02|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2019|12|31|df=y}}\n| <!--<ref name=\"auto\"/>-->\n|-\n! [[Holby City (series 21)|22]]\n| TBD{{Refn|Filming on Holby City was suspended on 18 March 2020 due to the [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United Kingdom|coronavirus pandemic]].|group=nb}}\n| {{Start date|2020|01|07|df=y}}\n| TBD\n| <!--<ref name=\"auto\"/>-->\n|}\n\n== Notes ==\n{{reflist|group=\"nb\"}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n{{Wikiquote}}\